data.description: Welcome to this stunning single family home located in the desirable community of Ashford in Waldorf, MD. Offering an array of features and amenities, this property is sure to capture your attention and make you envision a life of comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the open floor plan, which creates a seamless flow throughout the home. The spacious living area boasts high ceilings and beautiful wood flooring, adding a touch of elegance to the space. With four bedrooms, there's plenty of room for the whole family, and the walk-in closets provide ample storage. The fully equipped kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with modern appliances including a refrigerator, microwave, range, disposal, and oven. The adjacent eating space is perfect for casual dining or entertaining guests. Additionally, the laundry room makes everyday chores a breeze. Enjoy the warmth and coziness of the gas fireplace during chilly evenings. The central heating and cooling system ensures year-round comfort, while the central air keeps the home fresh and cool during warmer months. Outside, you'll find a 2-car garage and on-street parking for your convenience. The property sits on a .29-acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities or gardening.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this house your dream home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this Waldorf gem yours!
